title: Neff & The Seventh Letter Present: Sesame Street
description: Neff Headwear and The Seventh Letter collaborate to bring the Sesame Street Art Show. A one of a kind art presentation bringing together 40 of the best street artists from around the world creating works of art inspired by their favorite Sesame Street characters. The show was held at the Known Gallery in Los Angeles, California. A portion of the proceeds benefited City of Hope Department of Pediatrics.
